resources.string: Committed to sharing and spreading STEM knowledge among the student community. Help students become standouts by providing them training and inspiration unavailable in the confines of their classrooms. Regularly organizes university and global level events like workshops, entrepreneurship events and hackathons.

Team Fourth Dimension is the Technical Division of IET-VIT. The team of enthusiasts who pique their interest in everything happening about technology. The team is actively involved in various projects spread across multiple domains as Blockchain, Robotics, App & Web development, Machine Learning & Artificial Intelligence. The team has a legacy of achieving, having numerous achievements globally.
